OL,3,CFlytippers dump 'lorry load' of waste
OL,4,Cblocking road
OL,6,FA road in Lichfield has been blocked
OL,7,Fafter fly-tippers dumped large amounts
OL,8,Fof rubbish there.
OL,10,FBusinesses and residents have been
OL,11,Funable to use Watery Lane in Lichfield
OL,12,Fafter a "lorry load" of waste was left
OL,13,Fon the road.
OL,15,FPolice were called to the lane at
OL,16,F6.15am this morning. Staffordshire
OL,17,FPolice have closed off the road access
OL,18,Fthrough Eastern Avenue and Wood End
OL,19,FLane. Lichfield District Council are
OL,20,Faware.
