OL,3,CFlytippers dump 'lorry load' of waste
OL,4,Cblocking road
OL,6,FFlytipping is the illegal dumping of
OL,7,Fliquid or solid waste in land or in
OL,8,Fwater. The waste is usually dumped to
OL,9,Favoid disposal costs.
OL,11,FThe pile of rubbish has blocked both
OL,12,Fsides of the road across a stretch
OL,13,Fcovering a number of metres and is at
OL,14,Fthe junction with Wood End Lane.
OL,16,FOne company owner in the area said:
OL,17,F"Not only have the individuals behind
OL,18,Fthis blocked the road for local
OL,19,Fresidents, but emergency services are
OL,20,Funable to get down there now.
