OL,3,CFlytippers dump 'lorry load' of waste
OL,4,Cblocking road
OL,6,F"And to add insult to injury, this is
OL,7,Fthe only road into the countryside
OL,8,Fcentre so you're stopping around 20
OL,9,Fsmall businesses from operating."
OL,11,FAnother business said this morning's
OL,12,Fincident was the latest blow to
OL,13,Fcompanies in the area.
OL,15,FThey said: "We have struggled for the
OL,16,Fpast 12 months to cope with the
OL,17,Fconstant road closures with the new
OL,18,Fhousing development and HS2 closing
OL,19,Fthe road to Lichfield under the
OL,20,Frailway bridge.
