OL,6,F"Due to the scale of the fly-tipping,
OL,7,Fwe immediately informed the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency. In the meantime,
OL,9,Four environmental health officers are
OL,10,Flooking for evidence whilst we make
OL,11,Farrangements to safely remove and
OL,12,Fdispose of the waste as soon as
OL,13,Fpossible."
OL,15,FAnyone with information on fly-tipping
OL,16,Fcan report it to Lichfield District
OL,17,FCouncil.
