OL,3,CFlytippers dump 'lorry load' of waste
OL,4,Cblocking road
OL,6,FFlytipping is a criminal offence in
OL,7,Fthe UK under the Environmental
OL,8,FProtection Act 1990.
OL,10,FThere are various punishments for
OL,11,Fflytipping including imprisonment,
OL,12,Funlimited fines as well as an order to
OL,13,Fdeprive rights to a vehicle used to
OL,14,Fcommit the offence.
OL,16,FLocal authorities usually deal with
OL,17,Fsmaller scale, more frequent incidents
OL,18,Fand the Environment Agency will deal
OL,19,Fwith larger scale, more serious
OL,20,Fincidents of illegal waste disposal.
